data.description: SHORTSALE/THIRD PARTY APPROVAL REQUIRED:   1,800 foot square townhome in the sought-after Montclair community.    The home entails three spacious bedrooms with a fourth in the basement that could be used as  a bedroom or an office.   Full bath in basement with a walk out to the back yard  Fireplace in basement.   Gorgeous deck backing nature and woods for exclusive privacy.     Modern kitchen and pantry.  2 assigned parking spaces with guests parking available.    Convenient to dynamic shops,  movies, dining, and entertainment.     Close to Quantico Marine Base and Fort Belvoir Army Base.  Convenient commuter lots/transportation to Washington, DC and Pentagon so that you can relax before work.   Bring in the New Year right in this stunning home!  Staged furniture is no longer inside of home.
